HansTech0.text: body {     font-family: Arial, sans-serif;     margin: 0;     padding: 0; } header {     background: #333;     color: white;     padding: 1em;     text-align: center; } main {     padding: 1em; } button {     background: #28a745;     border: none;     color: white;     padding: 0.5em 1em;     cursor: pointer; } button:hover {     background: #218838; } input {     display: block;     margin: 0.5em 0;     padding: 0.5em;     width: calc(100% - 120px);     float: left; } .input-area {     overflow: hidden; } #chat-box {     border: 1px solid #ccc;     height: 300px;     overflow-y: auto;     padding: 1em;     margin-bottom: 1em;     background: #f9f9f9; } .message {     margin: 0.5em 0;     padding: 0.5em 1em;     border-radius: 15px;     max-width: 70%;     display: inline-block;     clear: both; } .message.sent {     background: #dcf8c6;     float: right;     text-align: right; } .message.received {     background: #fff;     float: left;     text-align: left; }
